trans-unit.source: Represents a basic step that is displayed in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et grunnleggende trinn som vises i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control is made up of a collection of WizardStep objects that represent single steps of a wizard.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>kontrollen består av en samling av WizardStep-objekter som representerer enkle trinnene i en veiviser.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control displays a single WizardStep object at a time.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>kontrollen viser et enkeltobjekt WizardStep om gangen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>

trans-unit.source: You can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control and its associated WizardStep objects to collect related data in a linear or nonlinear fashion.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>kontrollen og tilknyttede WizardStep objektene til å samle inn relaterte data på en lineær eller ikke-lineære måte.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If you embed the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login> control in a WizardStep, explicitly set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.ActiveStepIndex%2A> in a `Page_Load` event handler if the user is authenticated.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis du bygger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>kontroll i en WizardStep, angis eksplisitt av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.ActiveStepIndex%2A>i en `Page_Load` hendelsesbehandlingen Hvis brukeren er godkjent.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.ActiveStepIndex%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Login>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control does not automatically advance to the next WizardStep in this scenario.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>kontrollen ikke automatisk gå videre til neste WizardStep i dette scenarioet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>

trans-unit.source: You cannot apply a theme to WizardStep but you can apply a theme to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ikke bruke et tema WizardStep, men du kan bruke et tema på <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If you programmatically add a WizardStep in the `Page_Load` event handler, you must add the navigation to that step prior to the page loading.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis du legger til en WizardStep i programmatisk den `Page_Load` hendelsesbehandling, må du legge til navigeringen dette trinnet før innlasting av siden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStep"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStep"> </xref> klasse.
